    <body>

        <div rend="parallel">
          <p xml:id="Kali15-kilavi">itu pirivuṇarttiya talaimakaṟkut, tōḻi, talaimakaḷatu āṟṟāmaiyum iḷamaiya 
            tarumaiyuṅ kūṟi, nīr pirintu ceyyak karutiyavai ekkālattuñ ceyyalām poruḷāṟ kaḻinta iḷamai 
            mīṭkalākumō-veṉak kūṟiyatu.</p>
          <p xml:lang="en">This is what the confidante told the hero, who informed [her] of the separation, talking about the inability of the heroine and the preciousness of youth, saying "will there be a return of youth that passed by because of the wealth when what you intend to make when separating is to be made any time?"</p>
        </div>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="Kali15">
                <l>arimā ṉiṭittaṉṉa vañcilai valviṟ</l>
                <l>purināṇ puṭaiyiṟ puṟaṅkāṇṭa lallā</l>
                <l>liṇaippaṭait tāṉai yaracō ṭuṟiṉuṅ</l>
                <l>kaṇaittoṭai nāṇuṅ kaṭuntuṭi yārppi</l>
                <l>ṉeruttu valiya veṟuḻnōk kiralai</l>
                <l>maruppiṟ ṟirintu maṟintuvīḻ tāṭi</l>
                <l>yurutta kaṭuñciṉat tōṭā maṟavar</l>
                <l>poruḷkoṇṭu puṇceyi ṉallatai yaṉpō</l>
                <l>ṭaruḷpuṟa māṟiya vāriṭai yattam;</l>
                <l rend="space">puripunī puṟamāṟip pōkkeṇṇip putitīṇṭip</l>
                <l>perukiya celvattāṟ peyarttara lolvatō</l>
                <l>ceyalaiyan taḷirēykku meḻiṉala mannalam</l>
                <l>payalaiyā luṇappaṭṭup paṇṭainī roḻintakkāl;</l>
                <l rend="space">poyyaṟṟa kēḷviyāṟ puraiyōraip paṭarntunī</l>
                <l>maiyaṟṟa paṭivattāṉ maṟuttara lolvatō</l>
                <l>tīṅkatir matiyēykkun tirumuka mammukam</l>
                <l>pāmpucēr matipōlap pacappūrntu tolaintakkāl;</l>
                <l rend="space">piṉṉiya toṭarnīvip piṟarnāṭṭup paṭarntunī</l>
                <l>maṉṉiya puṇarcciyāṉ maṟuttara lolvatō</l>
                <l>puriyaviḻ naṟunīlam puraiyuṇkaṇ kaluḻpāṉāt</l>
                <l>tiriyumiḻ neyyēpōṟ ṟeṇpaṉi yuṟaikkuṅkāl;</l>
                <l rend="space">eṉavāṅku,</l>
                <l>aṉaiyavai pōṟṟi niṉaiiyaṉa nāṭikkāṇ</l>
                <l>vaḷamaiyō vaikaluñ ceyalāku maṟṟivaṇ</l>
                <l>muḷainirai muṟuvalā rāyattu ḷeṭuttāynta</l>
                <l>viḷamaiyun taruvatō viṟanta piṉṉē.</l>
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l corresp="9">            The road is a difficult way devoid of grace </l>
<l corresp="8">and love unless [deadly] wounds are made when taking wealth </l>
<l corresp="7">by bold men who do not run, with furious fierce anger, </l>
<l>with hanging beards ?</l>
<l rend="indent"><note>Lines 3-6 incomprehensible.</note></l>
<l corresp="2">besides seeing the outside of the side of the twisted string </l>
<l corresp="1">of the strong bow of pretty Cilai wood that roars like a lion, </l>
<l rend="space">You reckoning to go, acting and avoiding, is it possible to return</l>
<l>with wealth that is increased by newly gathering [it]</l>
<l>– at the time [her] former disposition has ceased, that beauty having been consumed </l>
<l>by pallor, a graceful beauty that resembled the pretty sprouts of Aśoka?</l>
<l rend="space">You setting out for people great with leaning that is free from falsehood,</l>
<l>will it be possible to restore it to [its] form free from blemish</l>
<l>at the time when that face is lost, crept over by pallor like the moon</l>
<l>joined by the snake, [her] brilliant face that resembled the sweet-rayed moon?</l>
<l rend="space">You setting out for the land of others, stroking [her] braided tresses,</l>
<l>will it be possible to restore [them] by lasting union</l>
<l>– at the time clear tears drip like ghee emitted by the wick,</l>
<l>unendingly, as [her] kajal eyes weep that were like fragrant blue lotus that opens [its] strands? </l>
<l rend="space">That is to say,</l>
<l rend="space">paying attention to such things examine [your] thoughts, see:</l>
<l>as for riches, is it possible to make [them] daily? After it has passed,</l>
<l>will it bring [back] her youth that was held up [and] selected</l>
<l>among [her] companions of smiling girls [with teeth] in sprout[-like] rows?  </l>

            </lg>
        </div>
